Transcription.Text: And it is as well to wear goggles - your motor-cycle goggles will serve admirably - when pieces of metal are likely to be flying about. Petrol, or any other inflammable liquid, should be removed from the working area, for a spark from a grinding or sanding wheel can start a fire.
